(134, 1, '2018-07-19 11:05:38', '2018-07-19 11:05:38', 'The brainchild of Haresh Pahuja and in collaboration with Sudesh Pahuja and Arun Pahuja in India, Itan is powered by the strength of over four decades of experience and expertise in the jewellery industry.\n\nInspired by the Sioux word for ‘chief’, Itan represents the marriage of traditional values and contemporary learnings, introducing a refined approach that establishes us as a pioneer in the gold market. By creating harmony between delicate craftsmanship and new-age technology, we design exquisite bangles that transcend tradition and trend.', 'Itan Jewels DMCC', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'itan-jewels-dmcc', '', '', '2018-07-19 11:05:38', '2018-07-19 11:05:38', '', 0, 'https://try.chethemes.com/jobhunt/?post_type=company&amp;p=134', 0, 'company', '', 0),
