(24, 1, '2018-07-18 12:09:36', '2018-07-18 12:09:36', '<h3>Job Description</h3>\nObjectives: Responsible for implementing the supply chain and logistics operations in Qatar. Coordinate with logistics and warehouse operations employees to direct daily supply chain operations. Ensure timely receipt of products from supplier to the stores, food and beverage outlets, and customers in accordance with purchase order requirements while ensuring the monitoring and management of all logistics functions. Ensure optimal inventory levels are maintained.', 'Supply Chain Manager', '', 'expired', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'supply-chain-manager', '', '', '2024-05-26 11:38:30', '2024-05-26 11:38:30', '', 0, 'https://try.chethemes.com/jobhunt/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=24', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
