(56, 1, '2018-07-18 14:44:17', '2018-07-18 14:44:17', '<h3>Job Description</h3>\nWe are looking for a well-rounded Senior UX Designer to join our Commerce Applications Tribe in Montevideo to deliver the end-to-end experience of the Commerce suite.\n\nWorking with dedicated and passionate scrum teams, we expect you to help the team shape the product experience around the customers and users, streamlining workflows and optimizing business processes.', 'Senior UX Designer', '', 'expired', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'senior-ux-designer', '', '', '2024-05-26 11:38:29', '2024-05-26 11:38:29', '', 0, 'https://try.chethemes.com/jobhunt/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=56', -1, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(58, 1, '2018-07-18 14:51:54', '2018-07-18 14:51:54', '<h3>Job Description</h3>\nFront End Software Engineer (Angular) - Athens Morson International are recruiting for a Front End Software Engineer to join a well-established software house in Athens. The Software Engineer will be working with large amounts of data flowing through the system while securing applications from external abuses. The Front End Software Engineer will be developing the backend of a new WebAPI, implementing the front end software using Angular and testing the functionality using MS SQL. The Front End Software Engineer will be working within a fast paced environment, work under exceptional management and have the chance to really push forward within their career. The successful Front End Software Developer will have: - 4+ years\' experience as a software engineer - Strong technical knowledge in current web development technologies - HTML, CSS and JavaScript - Experience using Angular (2.0+) - Experience working with Microsoft .Net C# Nice to have skills: - Experience collaborating on software projects with design and API aspects - Worked on applications with modern stack (ES2015, Flexbox, CSS Modules) - Experience working with ASP.Net Core - Experience working with Elixir This is an excellent opportunity for you to really push on in your career with the amount of opportunities that are available. You will be working alongside some highly technical engineers who have a passion for what they do. If you are interested, apply now and I will be in touch shortly. Alternatively, contact Jake from Morson for more information', 'Front End Developer', '', 'expired', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'front-end-software-engineer-athens', '', '', '2024-05-26 11:38:29', '2024-05-26 11:38:29', '', 0, 'https://try.chethemes.com/jobhunt/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=58', 0, 'job_listing', '', 0),
(61, 1, '2018-07-18 14:57:30', '2018-07-18 14:57:30', '<h3>Job Description</h3>\nLine of Business: Financial Services Position: Networking Engineer Project Description We are working on bringing modern telecommunication solutions to our customers providing professional services enables large-scale digital transformations, unlocking the opportunities of the cloud, virtualization and the changing mobile ecosystem. We are looking for Networking Engineer to join our team to take part in digital transformation projects. Responsibilities - Design Network aspects of the project - Participation in validation of Solution Design - Discussing with the customer network implementation aspects - Perform network implementation of the project Planning: - Elaborate the requirements - Create configuration templates for network devices and scripts for automated deployment - Define implementation procedures - Scheduling implementation steps with the customers team Execution: - Deploy, connect, configure and test network devices Skills 3-5 of experience in implementation of Network solutions within Digital Transformation projects Networking skills: Operational and Design Skills (experience with Juniper solutions appreciated) RedHat, Ubuntu, Scripting (e.g. Perl, Python, shell)', 'Networking Engineer', '', 'expired', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'networking-engineer', '', '', '2024-05-26 11:38:29', '2024-05-26 11:38:29', '', 0, 'https://try.chethemes.com/jobhunt/?post_type=job_listing&#038;p=61', -1, 'job_listing', '', 0),
